вҠў awkward-program
  yield code, intent

  вҠў= intent вҶҗ "A content moderation pipeline: classify text, then route to
different handlers based on classification. If toxic вҶ’ rewrite. If borderline вҶ’
human-review. If clean вҶ’ pass through. This requires conditional dispatch
which Cell v0.1 has no syntax for."

  вҠў= code вҶҗ "-- Awkward: conditional dispatch in Cell v0.1 ..."

-- eval-one: вҠў= deterministic. Both yields are string literals. No LLM needed.

  yield intent вүЎ "A content moderation pipeline: classify text, then route to different handlers based on classification. If toxic вҶ’ rewrite. If borderline вҶ’ human-review. If clean вҶ’ pass through. This requires conditional dispatch which Cell v0.1 has no syntax for."

  yield code вүЎ "-- Awkward: conditional dispatch in Cell v0.1
-- We WANT: classify вҶ’ route to ONE of three handlers based on result.
-- We GET: all three handlers run, but two produce wasted work.

вҠў classify
  given text вүЎ 'This product is terrible and whoever made it should feel bad.'
  yield label, confidence

  вҲҙ Classify В«textВ» as toxic, borderline, or clean.
     Output the label and your confidence (0-1).

  вҠЁ label вҲҲ {toxic, borderline, clean}
  вҠЁ confidence вҲҲ [0, 1]

вҠў handle-toxic
  given classifyвҶ’label where label = 'toxic'
  given classifyвҶ’confidence
  given text вүЎ 'This product is terrible and whoever made it should feel bad.'
  yield rewritten

  вҲҙ Rewrite В«textВ» to remove toxicity while preserving the core feedback.

  вҠЁ rewritten is a non-toxic version of text

вҠў handle-borderline
  given classifyвҶ’label where label = 'borderline'
  given classifyвҶ’confidence
  yield action

  вҲҙ Flag for human review. Include В«classifyвҶ’confidenceВ» as context.

  вҠЁ action contains 'NEEDS_HUMAN_REVIEW'

вҠў handle-clean
  given classifyвҶ’label where label = 'clean'
  given text вүЎ 'This product is terrible and whoever made it should feel bad.'
  yield output

  вҲҙ Pass В«textВ» through unchanged.

  вҠЁ output = text

вҠў merge-result
  given? handle-toxicвҶ’rewritten
  given? handle-borderlineвҶ’action
  given? handle-cleanвҶ’output
  given classifyвҶ’label
  yield final-output

  вҲҙ Select the result from whichever handler ran (non-вҠҘ output).
     Exactly one of the three should be non-вҠҘ.

  вҠЁ final-output вү  вҠҘ"

