--   The program validates that v0.2's feature set is compositionally complete
--   for the conditional-dispatch use case.
--
-- вҠў= Observation 2: guard-gated dispatch replaces conditional output cells
--   R16's compile-changes handled both clean and not-clean cases in a single
--   cell with a conditional вҲҙ body ("If is-clean is true, compile... If NOT
--   clean, state which awkwardnesses remain..."). R17 splits this into two
--   cells with mutually exclusive guards: compile-changes (is-clean = true)
--   and iterate-further (is-clean = false). Exactly one fires. The skipped
--   cell produces вҠҘ. This is the same pattern the program discovers for
--   content moderation вҖ” proof that guard clauses generalize.
--
-- вҠў= Observation 3: вҠўвҲҳ converges in 1 iteration because the problem is pre-solved
--   The R16 version would have found awkwardness-score вүҲ 4+ (no guard clauses,
--   N/A hack, wasted computation). The R17 version finds awkwardness-score =
--   2.3 because the embedded fragment already uses guards. The вҠўвҲҳ loop still
--   does useful work: it identifies the wildcard composition pattern and
--   confirms the remaining awkwardness is cosmetic (severity 2). A вҠўвҲҳ loop
--   that converges in 1 iteration is not wasted вҖ” it CERTIFIES the result.
--
-- вҠў= Observation 4: В§-quotation enables meta-level spec evolution
--   В§awkward-program passes the cell definition as data to identify-awkwardness,
--   which analyzes the code structure rather than executing it. This is the
--   code-as-data pattern that makes Cell's meta-programming possible. The
--   quotation system, unchanged from v0.1, composes cleanly with all v0.2
--   additions вҖ” guard clauses, wildcards, given?, and вҠҘ propagation.
--
-- вҠў= Observation 5: the вҠў= expression language is self-consistent here
--   All hard cells (spec-excerpt, awkward-program, obs-*) use string literals.
--   Guard clauses use equality comparisons (is-clean = true, is-clean = false).
--   evaluate-improvement's oracles use arithmetic comparison (1.4 вүӨ 2.3).
--   No false crystallization вҖ” every вҠў= body uses only v0.2 defined primitives.
--   The awkwardness-score oracle (вҠЁ awkwardness-score = mean of all severities)
--   is semantic (requires understanding what "mean" means in context), but this
