-- вҠў= Observation 6: v0.2 feature composition is the real spec evolution
--   The program proposes zero new syntax. Guard clauses, wildcard deps, given?,
--   and вҠҘ propagation вҖ” all existing v0.2 features вҖ” compose to solve the
--   conditional-dispatch problem that motivated program 30 in R16. The insight:
--   v0.2's features are NOT independent additions. They form a compositional
